data.description: Great news! The previous buyer got cold feet so now YOU can make this YOUR home!    Welcome to 569 Greenfield Ct, a charming residence nestled in the beautiful city of Upland. This meticulously maintained home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Our seller has recently added a new roof, new HVAC and new water heater.     As you step through the front door, you are greeted by an inviting living room adorned with abundant natural light and a beautiful fireplace. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living room to the modern kitchen, complete with a center island with a granite waterfall countertop, creating an ideal setting for entertaining friends and family.    The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinet space, catering to both the aspiring chef and daily meal preparation. Enjoy casual meals at the breakfast bar or savor special occasions in the adjacent eating area.    The home features 4 bedrooms, each providing a tranquil retreat. The primary suite is a haven of relaxation, complete with an en suite bathroom.    Step outside to discover the private backyard oasis which boasts a private pool and firepit – perfect for al fresco dining, gardening, or simply unwinding after a long day.     Additional highlights include new roof, new HVAC system, & new water heater. Conveniently located just minutes from the 10fwy, schools, parks, and shopping.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm of 569 Greenfield Ct, where comfort meets style.
